\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 5. A. aegaea} Turrill, {\i  Kew Bull.}{\b  1939}: 189 (1939). Like {\b 4}, but leaflets very narrowly elliptical to linear, often revolute; heads with fewer (5-9) flowers; calyx 6·5-9 mm. •{\i   Kriti and Kikladhes }({\i  Pholegandros, Amorgos}). Cr Gr.
